{"type":null,"faqId":14582,"title":"手机待机时间短，耗电快，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开启省电模式：进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>省电管理</b>，根据需要选择省电模式为<b>智能省电</b>或<b>超级省电</b>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span><img width=\"558\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828165754903001.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">清理后台暂不使用的应用程序。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不使用手机时，请关闭屏幕。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">缩短屏幕待机时间。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">降低屏幕亮度。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">降低音量。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不使用移动网络、蓝牙、</span><span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span> GPS </span><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;\">时，请关闭对应功能。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级手机，以体验更好的手机性能。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">若您认为手机待机时间过短，已影响正常使用，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":1,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6642","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1409216279000,"seriesProductName":"Holly-T00,Holly-U10","visitedTimes":663,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}